    %h2 What information do we collect?
    %ul
      %li
        %strong Information from your use of our services.
        We collect information from you when you Sign In with OAuth.  (This means your login credentials at Twitter, Facebook, LinkedIn, Youtube, and other networks you can choose to connect with Mashoutable™ are not accessed nor stored by Mashoutable™.

      %li
